msg.msgText:
A "CertificateProfile" composite object can be deleted using the "delete" option of the "imaserver" command.
SYNTAX: imaserver delete CertificateProfile help imaserver delete CertificateProfile "Name=value"
EXAMPLE: imaserver delete CertificateProfile "Name=CertProfile"
